{"tid":784143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★運輸署60萬攪App未能查巴士到站時間，強調特點是無廣告！","createTime":"2018-08-18T06:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T08:12:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"62152acb715eff8f928177ef98afba45e11a384a","tid":784143,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:44:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府App特色：「無廣告」交通資訊</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「香港出行易」HKeMobility 是運輸署製作的一站式交通流動應用程式，花費六十萬港元製作。提供實時交通及運輸資訊，並鼓勵步行，而且關懷不同需要人士，提供交通消息朗讀功能。問到與現存的路線搜尋應用程式有何分別，高級工程師（智慧出行）區家傑指：「這個手機 App 將我們的資訊連繫起來，可將交通、乘車路線帶到市民身邊。同坊間手機 App 分別是，它會整合不同交通工具，作出最好的建議。<span style=\"color: red;\">另一特點是，我從未講過的，就是此手機 App 並無廣告</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/unwire0000-33-694x382.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Funwire0000-33-694x382.png&h=b424244b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/08/18/hkemobility/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2Fhkemobility%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=n%2F1b9%2BlpRibGc%2B7vlEcTXJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=889f8642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/08/18/hkemobility/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"7b2ed889489048a1eb8e07d7ccbb03a6a1236e4a","tid":784143,"uid":19454,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"另一特點是，我從未講過的，就是此手機 App 並無廣告<br />\n另一特點是，我從未講過的，就是此手機 App 並無廣告<br />\n另一特點是，我從未講過的，就是此手機 App 並無廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsuper IT tech.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69621346dbd93e2e511